info.name: nero-cli
info.summary: nero-cli is a simple CLI tool that streamlines the process of downloading Official InvokeAI release from github and running it on your local machine. It is designed to be a simple allow you to quickly and easily pull the latest version, specify version, or rollback if you need to.
